"碍法（指令（EU）2019/882第4(5)条）规定的强制性义务。本声明作为最佳实践自愿提"
"供。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:801
msgid "Exemption basis:"
msgstr "豁免依据："

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:803
msgid "Directive (EU) 2019/882, Article 4(5) - Microenterprise exemption"
msgstr "指令（EU）2019/882第4(5)条 - 微型企业豁免"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:807 includes/class-edg-statement.php:817
msgid "Technical reference:"
msgstr "技术参考："

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:814
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is a personal website with no commercial activity. Personal websites "
"are outside the scope of the European Accessibility Act (Directive (EU) "
"2019/882) and Directive (EU) 2016/2102. This statement is provided "
"voluntarily as a commitment to inclusive design, following W3C Accessibility "
"Guidelines."
msgstr ""
"个人网站 / 私人：无商业活动的个人网站不在欧洲无障碍法（指令（EU）2019/882）和"
"指令（EU）2016/2102的适用范围内。本声明自愿提供，作为对包容性设计的承诺。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:824
msgid ""
"This statement is prepared in compliance with the European Accessibility Act "
"(Directive (EU) 2019/882, applicable from 28 June 2025) and applicable "
"national implementing legislation. The technical requirements are based on "
"the harmonised standard EN 301 549 v3.2.1, which incorporates Web Content "
"Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.2, Level AA. The structure of this "
"statement follows the W3C Accessibility Statement best practice as reference "
"model."
msgstr ""
"本声明依据《欧洲无障碍法》（指令（EU）2019/882，自2025年6月28日起适用）及适用"
"的国家实施立法准备。技术要求基于协调标准 EN 301 549 v3.2.1。本声明的结构以 "
"W3C 无障碍声明最佳实践作为参考模型。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:829
msgid "Directive (EU) 2019/882 - European Accessibility Act"
msgstr "指令（EU）2019/882 - 欧洲无障碍法（EAA）"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:849
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This website is <strong>%s</strong> with WCAG 2.2 Level AA and the "
"requirements of Directive (EU) 2016/2102. \"Partially conformant\" means "
"that some parts of the content do not yet fully conform to the accessibility "
"standard."
msgstr ""
"本网站与 WCAG 2.2 AA 级和指令（EU）2016/2102 的要求<strong>%s</strong>。\"部"
"分合规\"意味着部分内容尚未完全符合无障碍标准。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:858
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This website is <strong>%s</strong> with WCAG 2.2 Level AA. This statement "
"is provided voluntarily. \"Partially conformant\" means that some parts of "
"the content do not yet fully conform to the accessibility guidelines."
msgstr ""
"本网站与 WCAG 2.2 AA 级<strong>%s</strong>。本声明自愿提供。\"部分合规\"意味"
"着部分内容尚未完全符合无障碍指南。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:867
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This website is <strong>%s</strong> with WCAG 2.2 Level AA and the "
"requirements of Directive (EU) 2019/882 where applicable. \"Partially "
"conformant\" means that some parts of the content do not yet fully conform "
"to the accessibility standard."
msgstr ""
"本网站与 WCAG 2.2 AA 级和指令（EU）2019/882 的要求（适用范围内）<strong>%s</"
"strong>。\"部分合规\"意味着部分内容尚未完全符合无障碍标准。"

#: includes/class-edg-statement.php:876
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This website is <strong>%s</strong> with WCAG 2.2 Level AA and the "
"requirements of Directive (EU) 2019/882. \"Partially conformant\" means that "
"some parts of the content do not yet fully conform to the accessibility "
